{
  "page": "Alynne Connington",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Connington\" title=\"House Connington\"><img alt=\"House Connington.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/12/House_Connington.svg/50px-House_Connington.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/12/House_Connington.svg/75px-House_Connington.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/12/House_Connington.svg/100px-House_Connington.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Alynne Connington</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Connington\" title=\"House Connington\"><img alt=\"House Connington.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/12/House_Connington.svg/50px-House_Connington.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/12/House_Connington.svg/75px-House_Connington.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/12/House_Connington.svg/100px-House_Connington.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Connington\" title=\"House Connington\">House Connington</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Stormlander\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Stormlander\">Stormlander</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Ronald_Connington\" title=\"Ronald Connington\">Ronald Connington</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (appears)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Alynne Connington</b> is the younger sister of Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Ronnet_Connington\" title=\"Ronnet Connington\">Ronnet Connington</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Knight_of_Griffin%27s_Roost\" title=\"Knight of Griffin&#39;s Roost\">Knight of Griffin's Roost</a>. She resides in <a href=\"/index.php/Griffin%27s_Roost\" title=\"Griffin&#39;s Roost\">Griffin's Roost</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd61.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd61.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Family\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Family</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alynne_Connington&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alynne_Connington&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Alynne is made a captive when <a href=\"/index.php/Griffin%27s_Roost\" title=\"Griffin&#39;s Roost\">Griffin's Roost</a> is taken by <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Connington\" title=\"Jon Connington\">Jon Connington</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Company\" title=\"Golden Company\">Golden Company</a>, along with her brother <a href=\"/index.php/Raymund_Connington\" title=\"Raymund Connington\">Raymund</a> and their <a href=\"/index.php/Bastard\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bastard\">bastard</a> nephew <a href=\"/index.php/Ronald_Storm\" title=\"Ronald Storm\">Ronald Storm</a>. Jon feels that the three will make useful hostages should Ronnet attempt to retake the castle. When Jon orders that Alynne and the other young Conningtons be confined under guard, she begins to cry, and he tries to reassure her that no harm will come to her. That night, Jon has Alynne and the other young Conningtons as guests at the victory feast, in hopes of getting to know his relatives. However, when Ronald tells Jon that his father will kill him, Jon sends the children back to their cells.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd61.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd61.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alynne_Connington&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>No harm will come to any of you unless <a href=\"/index.php/Ronnet_Connington\" title=\"Ronnet Connington\">Red Ronnet</a> proves an utter fool.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd61.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd61.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Connington\" title=\"Jon Connington\">Jon Connington</a>, to Alynne, <a href=\"/index.php/Raymund_Connington\" title=\"Raymund Connington\">Raymund Connington</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Ronard_Storm\" title=\"Ronard Storm\">Ronard Storm</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alynne_Connington&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\">Lord<br /><a href=\"/index.php/House_Connington\" title=\"House Connington\">Connington</a></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\">Unknown<br />wife</td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td></tr><tr align=\"